OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780419954
OL,3,CChild dies and another in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A30 crash
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old boy has died and
OL,7,Fanother boy, aged five, is in a
OL,8,Fcritical condition following a crash
OL,9,Finvolving a number of vehicles on the
OL,10,FA30 in Cornwall.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,13,Fwestbound carriageway of the road near
OL,14,FConnor Downs just before 11am on
OL,15,FFriday 29 May. The boy died at the
OL,16,Fscene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
