FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780419954
OL,3,CChild dies and another in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A30 crash
OL,6,FThe other child was taken to Bristol
OL,7,FChildren's Hospital, a woman in her
OL,8,F70s who was seriously injured was
OL,9,Ftaken to Derriford Hospital, and a
OL,10,Fwoman in her 40s was taken to
OL,11,FDerriford Hospital and has since been
OL,12,Fdischarged.
OL,14,FBoth women and the boys were
OL,15,Ftravelling in the same car.
OL,17,FA local man in his 60s was arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,19,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,20,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
