OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780419954
OL,3,CChild dies and another in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A30 crash
OL,6,FHe was treated for minor injuries and
OL,7,Fhas been released while the
OL,8,Finvestigation continues.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police are
OL,11,Fappealing for witnesses and dash-cam
OL,12,Ffootage.
OL,14,FDetective inspector Andy Heath of the
OL,15,FSerious Collisions Investigation Team
OL,16,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with those who
OL,17,Fhave been affected by this incident.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
