OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780419954
OL,3,CChild dies and another in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A30 crash
OL,6,F"Specialists from the Roads Policing
OL,7,FTeam and Serious Collisions
OL,8,FInvestigation Team have continued
OL,9,Fenquiries through the weekend, and the
OL,10,Finvestigation team will be pursuing
OL,11,Fseveral lines of enquiry over the
OL,12,Fcoming weeks.
OL,14,F"It is not possible to provide details
OL,15,Fof the cause of the collision, and I
OL,16,Fwould ask the public not to speculate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
