PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780419954
OL,3,CChild dies and another in critical
OL,4,Ccondition after A30 crash
OL,6,F"Further information will be made
OL,7,Favailable in due course. Our priority
OL,8,Fat this time is to support those that
OL,9,Fhave been directly affected by this
OL,10,Ftragic incident and to secure the
OL,11,Fevidence required for a thorough
OL,12,Finvestigation."
OL,14,F"If you witnessed the collision or
OL,15,Fwere in the area with a dash-cam and
OL,16,Fhave not yet spoken to police, please
OL,17,Fcall 101 or make contact via our
OL,18,Fwebsite quoting 50260136471."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]
